Joshfire docs
-------------

Doc is available online at http://framework.joshfire.com/doc/

This README describes doc guidelines and how to contribute


How to launch
-------------

Checkout https://github.com/joshfire/www-joshfire next to your joshfire install, 
go in the www-joshfire directory and launch the local server with:

$ fab serve

You should be able to go at http://localhost:40009/doc/ and test your changes

JS API auto-generated doc :
$ fab jsdoc
result goes in docs/api/

Doc guidelines
--------------

 - Stay concise! Omit needless words.
 - Never use "we" or "us", always take a neutral tone
 - Use "Joshfire" or "the framework"

 

Thanks for contributing!